indicator.description:
(1)A new model of meaningful engagement with CSOs is created;
(2)Number of capacity  building for institutions in East Jerusalem ;
(3) Quality and quantity of CSOs services increased.
(4) Linkages between different institutions enhanced; 
(5) Different synergies and dialogues are created.

baseline.comment:
(1) Political complexity resulting from occupation and no model of engagement with CSOs;
(2)Limited capacity for the institutions in East Jerusalem;  
(3)Weak and fragmented services; 
(4)Lack of linkages between the different institutions; 
(5)Limited synergies and dialogue among CSOs.
